reconstruction projects in Iran.
   The North Korean daily Rodong Shinmun said: ``The Korean people
will steadily develop friendly and cooperative relations with
Iran'' in their common struggle against ``imperialism in ideas of
independence, peace and friendship,'' according to the North Korean
