<HEAD>Scottish Extremists Claim Fire Was Anti-Nuclear Protest</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Scottish nationalists blew up a stone-crushing
plant because the quarry where it was located was going to be used
